"Eyyahhh!" Inferno yelled as the acid spikes stuck in him and his 
metal sizzled. Using his free hand he pulled one out while taking off 
into the air.

Quickstrike got up "Oh who hit me?" he groned.

Waspinator flew above the bots "Waspinator see target" he said as he 
loaded his weapon with an explosive stinger and fired it at Burrock.
